DESCRIPTION:
------------
This configuration works if you store you music as follow:
 - Like the "default" configuration but with a single dot as separator (with an optional space)
    - For the album folder between year and name
	- For songs files between number and title


TREE STRUCTURE:
---------------
example-tree/
|-- Alice
|   |-- 2000.First Album
|   |   |-- 01.Track One.mp3
|   |   |-- 02.Track Two.mp3
|   |   |-- 03.Track Three.mp3
|   |   |-- cover.jpg
|   |   `-- playlist.m3u
|   `-- 2001. Second Album
|       |-- 01. Track One.mp3
|       |-- 02. Track Two.mp3
|       |-- 03. Track Three.mp3
|       |-- cover.jpg
|       `-- playlist.m3u
`-- Bob
    `-- The Album
        |-- 01.Track One.mp3
        |-- 02.Track Two.mp3
        `-- 03.Track Three.mp3

